summary: CONSUMER STATES THAT CHILD'S FINGER BECAME STUCK IN PLASTIC CLIPS THAT HOLDS 5-PT HARNESS STRAPS IN PLACE.  CONSUMER BELIEVES THAT CLIPS HAVE PINCH POINTS WHICH CAUSED SERIOUS SWELLING AND BLISTERING OF CHILD'S FINGER.  CSS INFO:  COSCO/02-531BNP/04-12-01                                 PH
